-----------------list of tasks-----------------------------
task : InsertingDocumentInMongoDB

Short Desc : insert user inputs  in databse

Long Desc : this task will allow you to get data from the html input using 'angularJS' then handle
        it with the 'express node.js framework' wich  will get it then insert it in "MongoDB" Databse.
        then  express   will return the inserted document and send to angular JS wich will
        display it to the user.

step 1 file  : /public/index.html


